Package com.example.indeedgambling

Class FirebaseViewModel

java.lang.Object
androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
com.example.indeedgambling.FirebaseViewModel
public class FirebaseViewModel extends androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
Firebase ViewModel responsible for handling all Firestore operations including profiles, events, invitations, notifications, images, and logs. It also provides LiveData streams for real-time UI updates and helper methods for CRUD operations and waiting list functionality.
